msgctxt "148_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, I should probably get going."
msgstr "Well, I should probably get going."

msgctxt "160_Date"
msgid "Be careful out there, Kiryu."
msgstr "Ten cuidado ahí fuera, Kiryu."

msgctxt "172_Kiryu"
msgid "I will."
msgstr "Lo haré."

msgctxt "208_Date"
msgid "What's the deal, Kiryu? Sounded like you came to some kind\r\n"
"of agreement?"
msgstr "What's the deal, Kiryu? Sounded like you came to some kind\r\n"
"of agreement?"

msgctxt "220_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, I'm meeting him with the file on the roof of Kamurocho\r\n"
"Hills. Tonight at ten... alone."
msgstr "Yeah, I'm meeting him with the file on the roof of Kamurocho\r\n"
"Hills. Tonight at ten... alone."

msgctxt "232_Tanimura"
msgid "Alone!? But that's insane!"
msgstr "Alone!? But that's insane!"

msgctxt "244_Date"
msgid "You're not actually going through with that baloney, are\r\n"
"you?"
msgstr "You're not actually going through with that baloney, are\r\n"
"you?"

msgctxt "256_Kiryu"
msgid "I have to. That's part of the deal."
msgstr "I have to. That's part of the deal."

msgctxt "268_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds like I'll be fighting through the entire Ueno Seiwa\r\n"
"Clan to get up there, too."
msgstr "Sounds like I'll be fighting through the entire Ueno Seiwa\r\n"
"Clan to get up there, too."

msgctxt "280_Akiyama"
msgid "Guy doesn't take any chances once he gets down to business,\r\n"
"huh? You sure you still wanna go?"
msgstr "Guy doesn't take any chances once he gets down to business,\r\n"
"huh? You sure you still wanna go?"

msgctxt "292_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm sure. There's no other way."
msgstr "I'm sure. There's no other way."

msgctxt "304_Date"
msgid "You say that, but..."
msgstr "You say that, but..."

msgctxt "316_Akiyama"
msgid "Let him go if he wants to go. Besides, I don't think\r\n"
"anything we say is gonna change his mind."
msgstr "Let him go if he wants to go. Besides, I don't think\r\n"
"anything we say is gonna change his mind."

msgctxt "328_Akiyama"
msgid "Isn't that right, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr "Isn't that right, Kiryu-san?"

msgctxt "340_Kiryu"
msgid "Right. A deal's a deal."
msgstr "Right. A deal's a deal."

msgctxt "412_Katsuragi"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "424_Kiryu"
msgid "You there, Katsuragi?"
msgstr "You there, Katsuragi?"

msgctxt "436_Katsuragi"
msgid "You're not Tanimura."
msgstr "You're not Tanimura."

msgctxt "448_Kiryu"
msgid "My name's Kiryu. I needed to talk to you, so I'm borrowing\r\n"
"Tanimura's phone for a bit."
msgstr "My name's Kiryu. I needed to talk to you, so I'm borrowing\r\n"
"Tanimura's phone for a bit."

msgctxt "460_Katsuragi"
msgid "Kiryu? As in the Tojo Clan Fourth Chairman, Kazuma\r\n"
"Kiryu-san?"
msgstr "Kiryu? As in the Tojo Clan Fourth Chairman, Kazuma\r\n"
"Kiryu-san?"

msgctxt "472_Kiryu"
msgid "That's the one."
msgstr "Así es."

msgctxt "484_Katsuragi"
msgid "Well, well, well. What a nice little surprise. So, what can\r\n"
"I do for you?"
msgstr "Well, well, well. What a nice little surprise. So, what can\r\n"
"I do for you?"

msgctxt "496_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm calling about Taiga and Yasuko Saejima."
msgstr "I'm calling about Taiga and Yasuko Saejima."

msgctxt "508_Katsuragi"
msgid "Oh? I don't know what you're talking about."
msgstr "Oh? I don't know what you're talking about."

msgctxt "520_Kiryu"
msgid "Drop the act. We know you took them from Purgatory."
msgstr "Drop the act. We know you took them from Purgatory."

msgctxt "532_Katsuragi"
msgid "And what of it?"
msgstr "And what of it?"

msgctxt "544_Kiryu"
msgid "I want to cut a deal with you. I have something you want\r\n"
"very badly. I'm sure of it."
msgstr "I want to cut a deal with you. I have something you want\r\n"
"very badly. I'm sure of it."

msgctxt "556_Katsuragi"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "568_Kiryu"
msgid "The file Hamazaki stole from Penitentiary No. 2 when he and\r\n"
"Saejima broke out."
msgstr "The file Hamazaki stole from Penitentiary No. 2 when he and\r\n"
"Saejima broke out."

msgctxt "580_Kiryu"
msgid "I can't help but assume you want it back. But maybe I'm\r\n"
"wrong."
msgstr "I can't help but assume you want it back. But maybe I'm\r\n"
"wrong."

msgctxt "592_Katsuragi"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "604_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds like you don't want it after all. Let's just forget\r\n"
"this ever happened. Later."
msgstr "Sounds like you don't want it after all. Let's just forget\r\n"
"this ever happened. Later."

msgctxt "616_Katsuragi"
msgid "Wait."
msgstr "Espera."

msgctxt "628_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "640_Katsuragi"
msgid "How did that file find its way into your hands?"
msgstr "How did that file find its way into your hands?"

msgctxt "652_Kiryu"
msgid "Good question. Hamazaki gave it to me down in Okinawa."
msgstr "Good question. Hamazaki gave it to me down in Okinawa."

msgctxt "664_Katsuragi"
msgid "...And who knows about all this?"
msgstr "...And who knows about all this?"

msgctxt "676_Kiryu"
msgid "Besides me and Hamazaki, just a few others who are here with\r\n"
"me now."
msgstr "Besides me and Hamazaki, just a few others who are here with\r\n"
"me now."

msgctxt "688_Katsuragi"
msgid "Munakata is in the dark?"
msgstr "Munakata is in the dark?"

msgctxt "700_Kiryu"
msgid "Munakata?"
msgstr "¿Munakata?"

msgctxt "712_Katsuragi"
msgid "Deputy commissioner of the Tokyo PD."
msgstr "Deputy commissioner of the Tokyo PD."

msgctxt "724_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. I don't see how he'd know."
msgstr "Yeah. I don't see how he'd know."

msgctxt "736_Katsuragi"
msgid "...Good. Well? Let's hear what you want."
msgstr "...Good. Well? Let's hear what you want."

msgctxt "748_Kiryu"
msgid "Taiga and Yasuko Saejima back safely. And the money Kido\r\n"
"stole from Sky Finance. Should be around a hundred billion."
msgstr "Taiga and Yasuko Saejima back safely. And the money Kido\r\n"
"stole from Sky Finance. Should be around a hundred billion."

msgctxt "760_Katsuragi"
msgid "For a living yakuza legend, you make a piss poor negotiator.\r\n"
"You're going to have to do better than that."
msgstr "For a living yakuza legend, you make a piss poor negotiator.\r\n"
"You're going to have to do better than that."

msgctxt "772_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "784_Katsuragi"
msgid "Negotiation is a psychological battle."
msgstr "Negotiation is a psychological battle."

msgctxt "796_Katsuragi"
msgid "If you can't entice the other party with terms that favor\r\n"
"them, you may as well pack up and go home."
msgstr "If you can't entice the other party with terms that favor\r\n"
"them, you may as well pack up and go home."

msgctxt "808_Katsuragi"
msgid "You understand, don't you?"
msgstr "You understand, don't you?"

msgctxt "820_Kiryu"
msgid "...Then what do you suggest?"
msgstr "...Then what do you suggest?"

msgctxt "832_Katsuragi"
msgid "What indeed... How about this?"
msgstr "What indeed... How about this?"

msgctxt "844_Katsuragi"
msgid "You come alone to make the exchange."
msgstr "You come alone to make the exchange."

msgctxt "856_Kiryu"
msgid "Alone?"
msgstr "Alone?"

msgctxt "868_Katsuragi"
msgid "You heard me. I'd like to see you bloodied and bruised by\r\n"
"the time you arrive, as well."
msgstr "You heard me. I'd like to see you bloodied and bruised by\r\n"
"the time you arrive, as well."

msgctxt "880_Kiryu"
msgid "What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué se supone que significa eso?"

msgctxt "892_Katsuragi"
msgid "I'm going to have you jump through a little hoop for me."
msgstr "I'm going to have you jump through a little hoop for me."

msgctxt "904_Katsuragi"
msgid "See if this old dog can still do a few tricks."
msgstr "See if this old dog can still do a few tricks."

msgctxt "916_Kiryu"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "928_Katsuragi"
msgid "We'll make the exchange on the Kamurocho Hills roof."
msgstr "We'll make the exchange on the Kamurocho Hills roof."

msgctxt "940_Katsuragi"
msgid "I'll be waiting there with Saejima, his sister, and the\r\n"
"hundred billion yen."
msgstr "I'll be waiting there with Saejima, his sister, and the\r\n"
"hundred billion yen."

msgctxt "952_Katsuragi"
msgid "All you'll need to do to reach the roof... is fight your way\r\n"
"through the entire Ueno Seiwa Clan."
msgstr "All you'll need to do to reach the roof... is fight your way\r\n"
"through the entire Ueno Seiwa Clan."

msgctxt "964_Kiryu"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "976_Katsuragi"
msgid "You might make your way up to the roof. You might die in the\r\n"
"process."
msgstr "You might make your way up to the roof. You might die in the\r\n"
"process."

msgctxt "988_Katsuragi"
msgid "It doesn't matter much to me either way."
msgstr "It doesn't matter much to me either way."

msgctxt "1000_Katsuragi"
msgid "Those are the terms I'd be willing to accept."
msgstr "Those are the terms I'd be willing to accept."

msgctxt "1012_Kiryu"
msgid "And if I make it up to the roof?"
msgstr "And if I make it up to the roof?"

msgctxt "1024_Katsuragi"
msgid "Then we move forward with the transaction."
msgstr "Then we move forward with the transaction."

msgctxt "1036_Katsuragi"
msgid "And I'll be secure in the knowledge that you'll be far too\r\n"
"exhausted to kill me."
msgstr "And I'll be secure in the knowledge that you'll be far too\r\n"
"exhausted to kill me."

msgctxt "1048_Katsuragi"
msgid "Even if you wanted to."
msgstr "Even if you wanted to."

msgctxt "1060_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1072_Katsuragi"
msgid "This is just how it has to be, Kiryu-san. I plan to live a\r\n"
"long, fulfilling life."
msgstr "This is just how it has to be, Kiryu-san. I plan to live a\r\n"
"long, fulfilling life."

msgctxt "1084_Katsuragi"
msgid "And taking my chances with monsters like you and Saejima...\r\n"
"Well, it would be nothing short of a fool's errand."
msgstr "And taking my chances with monsters like you and Saejima...\r\n"
"Well, it would be nothing short of a fool's errand."

msgctxt "1096_Katsuragi"
msgid "Not all yakuza are like Nishikiyama or Ryuji Goda."
msgstr "Not all yakuza are like Nishikiyama or Ryuji Goda."

msgctxt "1108_Katsuragi"
msgid "Some of us would rather survive than die atop the hill of\r\n"
"\"honor\" and \"manliness.\""
msgstr "Some of us would rather survive than die atop the hill of\r\n"
"\"honor\" and \"manliness.\""

msgctxt "1120_Katsuragi"
msgid "So, do we have a deal?"
msgstr "So, do we have a deal?"

msgctxt "1132_Kiryu"
msgid "Fine. I'll be there, just name the time."
msgstr "Fine. I'll be there, just name the time."

msgctxt "1144_Katsuragi"
msgid "Ten o'clock tonight."
msgstr "Ten o'clock tonight."

msgctxt "1156_Katsuragi"
msgid "I can only hope you still have a pulse by the time I see you\r\n"
"next."
msgstr "I can only hope you still have a pulse by the time I see you\r\n"
"next."

msgctxt "1168_Katsuragi"
msgid "Until then."
msgstr "Hasta entonces."

msgctxt "1228_Date"
msgid "How'd you end up with this thing, Kiryu?"
msgstr "How'd you end up with this thing, Kiryu?"

msgctxt "1240_Kiryu"
msgid "Hamazaki gave it to me down in Okinawa. It's a document\r\n"
"showing the creation of Penitentiary No. 2, and the expected\r\n"
"flow of money into the place."
msgstr "Hamazaki gave it to me down in Okinawa. It's a document\r\n"
"showing the creation of Penitentiary No. 2, and the expected\r\n"
"flow of money into the place."

msgctxt "1252_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh, will you look at that. It's got names, amounts,\r\n"
"everything."
msgstr "Huh, will you look at that. It's got names, amounts,\r\n"
"everything."

msgctxt "1264_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. It says right here that the ten billion yen that got\r\n"
"transferred from the Tojo to Kyohei Jingu back in 2005 was\r\n"
"meant to get passed on to the Metropolitan Police."
msgstr "Yeah. It says right here that the ten billion yen that got\r\n"
"transferred from the Tojo to Kyohei Jingu back in 2005 was\r\n"
"meant to get passed on to the Metropolitan Police."

msgctxt "1276_Tanimura"
msgid "That's the incident you were wrapped up in, right,\r\n"
"Kiryu-san?"
msgstr "That's the incident you were wrapped up in, right,\r\n"
"Kiryu-san?"

msgctxt "1288_Kiryu"
msgid "Right."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "1300_Kiryu"
msgid "That missing cash nearly tore the clan apart. And the guy\r\n"
"behind it all was a man named Kyohei Jingu. Haruka's father."
msgstr "That missing cash nearly tore the clan apart. And the guy\r\n"
"behind it all was a man named Kyohei Jingu. Haruka's father."

msgctxt "1312_Kiryu"
msgid "But there's more. There are notes on here detailing a police\r\n"
"plan to release inmates from Penitentiary No. 2 and create\r\n"
"artificial crime. All to make the police look good."
msgstr "But there's more. There are notes on here detailing a police\r\n"
"plan to release inmates from Penitentiary No. 2 and create\r\n"
"artificial crime. All to make the police look good."

msgctxt "1324_Date"
msgid "That's one hell of a scoop."
msgstr "That's one hell of a scoop."

msgctxt "1336_Tanimura"
msgid "No wonder they're so desperate to get it back. This goes\r\n"
"public, all their dirty laundry'll be out in the open."
msgstr "No wonder they're so desperate to get it back. This goes\r\n"
"public, all their dirty laundry'll be out in the open."

msgctxt "1348_Date"
msgid "So what's your next move?"
msgstr "So what's your next move?"

msgctxt "1360_Kiryu"
msgid "We try and cut a deal with Katsuragi. I just need to figure\r\n"
"out how to get in touch with him."
msgstr "We try and cut a deal with Katsuragi. I just need to figure\r\n"
"out how to get in touch with him."

msgctxt "1372_Tanimura"
msgid "I can help you with that. He and I have talked on the phone\r\n"
"before."
msgstr "I can help you with that. He and I have talked on the phone\r\n"
"before."

msgctxt "1384_Tanimura"
msgid "If you call from my cell, I'm sure he'll answer."
msgstr "If you call from my cell, I'm sure he'll answer."

msgctxt "1396_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. Mind if I borrow your phone, then?"
msgstr "Huh. Mind if I borrow your phone, then?"

msgctxt "1408_Tanimura"
msgid "Go right ahead."
msgstr "Sí..."

msgctxt "1456_Akiyama"
msgid "Life's a cruel mistress sometimes."
msgstr "Life's a cruel mistress sometimes."

msgctxt "1468_Akiyama"
msgid "Sure, you get used to the cheating and the backstabbing and\r\n"
"the lying in my line of work."
msgstr "Sure, you get used to the cheating and the backstabbing and\r\n"
"the lying in my line of work."

msgctxt "1480_Akiyama"
msgid "But when it all smacks you in the face one after another... Oof."
msgstr "But when it all smacks you in the face one after another... Oof."

msgctxt "1492_Date"
msgid "You seem like you're taking it pretty well, though."
msgstr "You seem like you're taking it pretty well, though."

msgctxt "1504_Date"
msgid "Most guys would go into total shock if they lost a hundred\r\n"
"grand, let alone a hundred billion."
msgstr "Most guys would go into total shock if they lost a hundred\r\n"
"grand, let alone a hundred billion."

msgctxt "1516_Akiyama"
msgid "I am in shock. This is me in shock."
msgstr "I am in shock. This is me in shock."

msgctxt "1528_Akiyama"
msgid "It's not that big of a deal, I know, but still."
msgstr "It's not that big of a deal, I know, but still."

msgctxt "1540_Date"
msgid "Not that big of a deal!?"
msgstr "Not that big of a deal!?"

msgctxt "1552_Akiyama"
msgid "I'll just make it all back again."
msgstr "I'll just make it all back again."

msgctxt "1564_Date"
msgid "But..."
msgstr "Pero..."

msgctxt "1576_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1588_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh."
msgstr "Je."

msgctxt "1600_Akiyama"
msgid "And hey, the week has had its highlights."
msgstr "And hey, the week has had its highlights."

msgctxt "1612_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh yeah?"
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "1624_Akiyama"
msgid "I met you for one, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "I met you for one, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "1636_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that really so special?"
msgstr "Is that really so special?"

msgctxt "1648_Akiyama"
msgid "You're my freaking hero, man. You saved my life."
msgstr "You're my freaking hero, man. You saved my life."

msgctxt "1660_Kiryu"
msgid "Did I? I think I'd remember that."
msgstr "Did I? I think I'd remember that."

msgctxt "1672_Akiyama"
msgid "Just listen. You know when the Millennium Tower blew up\r\n"
"five years ago? When all that cash rained down on the city?"
msgstr "Just listen. You know when the Millennium Tower blew up\r\n"
"five years ago? When all that cash rained down on the city?"

msgctxt "1684_Akiyama"
msgid "That day... changed my life. I grabbed as much as I could.\r\n"
"Cleaned myself up. Went from homeless bum to this in practically no time flat."
msgstr "That day... changed my life. I grabbed as much as I could.\r\n"
"Cleaned myself up. Went from homeless bum to this in practically no time flat."

msgctxt "1696_Akiyama"
msgid "If not for you, I'd still be out on the streets. Digging\r\n"
"through trash just to keep myself alive."
msgstr "If not for you, I'd still be out on the streets. Digging\r\n"
"through trash just to keep myself alive."

msgctxt "1708_Kiryu"
msgid "That's the money you built your business on, huh?"
msgstr "That's the money you built your business on, huh?"

msgctxt "1720_Akiyama"
msgid "Yup. Though now that I think about it..."
msgstr "Yup. Though now that I think about it..."

msgctxt "1732_Akiyama"
msgid "That ten billion was probably the same cash my bank duped me\r\n"
"into laundering for them before they had me take the fall."
msgstr "That ten billion was probably the same cash my bank duped me\r\n"
"into laundering for them before they had me take the fall."

msgctxt "1744_Kiryu"
msgid "The ten billion Jingu diverted to the Tojo Clan."
msgstr "The ten billion Jingu diverted to the Tojo Clan."

msgctxt "1756_Akiyama"
msgid "...So, yeah. This all feels kinda personal somehow."
msgstr "...So, yeah. This all feels kinda personal somehow."

msgctxt "1768_Akiyama"
msgid "If this stuff going down now is linked to that ten billion,\r\n"
"consider me there."
msgstr "If this stuff going down now is linked to that ten billion,\r\n"
"consider me there."

msgctxt "1804_Akiyama"
msgid "I dunno about you guys, but this is starting to feel like fate to me."
msgstr "I dunno about you guys, but this is starting to feel like fate to me."

msgctxt "1816_Akiyama"
msgid "Almost like we were all destined to end up here."
msgstr "Almost like we were all destined to end up here."

msgctxt "1828_Tanimura"
msgid "Fate?"
msgstr "Fate?"

msgctxt "1840_Date"
msgid "Hm."
msgstr "Hm."

msgctxt "1852_Kiryu"
msgid "You might just be right..."
msgstr "You might just be right..."

msgctxt "1888_Date"
msgid "You really think that's how it went down?"
msgstr "You really think that's how it went down?"

msgctxt "1900_Akiyama"
msgid "Can't think of any other way. Me and Hana-chan are the only\r\n"
"two people who knew about the vault."
msgstr "Can't think of any other way. Me and Hana-chan are the only\r\n"
"two people who knew about the vault."

msgctxt "1912_Akiyama"
msgid "Kido-chan's the only other possibility."
msgstr "Kido-chan's the only other possibility."

msgctxt "1924_Kiryu"
msgid "What makes you say that?"
msgstr "¿Qué le hace decir eso?"

msgctxt "1936_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, it would certainly wrap things up all nice and neat.\r\n"
"Everything would make sense."
msgstr "Well, it would certainly wrap things up all nice and neat.\r\n"
"Everything would make sense."

msgctxt "1948_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿A qué te refieres?"

msgctxt "1960_Akiyama"
msgid "Not long after Hana-chan saw him at the office, Kido-chan\r\n"
"got hauled off by Hatsushiba Clan boys, who'd been working\r\n"
"with the Shibata."
msgstr "Not long after Hana-chan saw him at the office, Kido-chan\r\n"
"got hauled off by Hatsushiba Clan boys, who'd been working\r\n"
"with the Shibata."

msgctxt "1972_Akiyama"
msgid "Just walked in and spirited him away. Simple. Clean."
msgstr "Just walked in and spirited him away. Simple. Clean."

msgctxt "1984_Kiryu"
msgid "What's so strange about that?"
msgstr "What's so strange about that?"

msgctxt "1996_Akiyama"
msgid "Everything. You'd understand if you've seen what Kido-chan\r\n"
"can do in a fight."
msgstr "Everything. You'd understand if you've seen what Kido-chan\r\n"
"can do in a fight."

msgctxt "2008_Date"
msgid "Go on."
msgstr "Dime."

msgctxt "2020_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, it's only been once I've witnessed it myself, but the\r\n"
"guy can mop the floor with anyone without even breaking a sweat."
msgstr "Well, it's only been once I've witnessed it myself, but the\r\n"
"guy can mop the floor with anyone without even breaking a sweat."

msgctxt "2032_Akiyama"
msgid "He's pretty coy about it, though. Prefers to keep all that\r\n"
"under wraps."
msgstr "He's pretty coy about it, though. Prefers to keep all that\r\n"
"under wraps."

msgctxt "2044_Date"
msgid "How come?"
msgstr "¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "2056_Kiryu"
msgid "It's better for the family that way."
msgstr "It's better for the family that way."

msgctxt "2068_Akiyama"
msgid "Most likely. Kanemura Enterprises, where Kido-chan and\r\n"
"Arai-san work, is a tiny speck under the big Shibata\r\n"
"umbrella."
msgstr "Most likely. Kanemura Enterprises, where Kido-chan and\r\n"
"Arai-san work, is a tiny speck under the big Shibata\r\n"
"umbrella."

msgctxt "2080_Akiyama"
msgid "Now your usual yakuza outfit makes their living off those\r\n"
"dramatic displays of strength... but not Kanemura."
msgstr "Now your usual yakuza outfit makes their living off those\r\n"
"dramatic displays of strength... but not Kanemura."

msgctxt "2092_Date"
msgid "Why not?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no?"

msgctxt "2104_Akiyama"
msgid "Didn't wanna stand out, especially with the rat race always\r\n"
"tearing this town apart. Guess that's just how he was."
msgstr "Didn't wanna stand out, especially with the rat race always\r\n"
"tearing this town apart. Guess that's just how he was."

msgctxt "2116_Tanimura"
msgid "Makes sense. It's safer to lay low and just get on with your\r\n"
"life than to start bashing heads in."
msgstr "Makes sense. It's safer to lay low and just get on with your\r\n"
"life than to start bashing heads in."

msgctxt "2128_Akiyama"
msgid "Yup. Kanemura couldn't even afford his dues to the Shibata.\r\n"
"Came to me begging for a loan and everything."
msgstr "Yup. Kanemura couldn't even afford his dues to the Shibata.\r\n"
"Came to me begging for a loan and everything."

msgctxt "2140_Akiyama"
msgid "Expanding his turf and inviting competition was probably the\r\n"
"last thing on his mind."
msgstr "Expanding his turf and inviting competition was probably the\r\n"
"last thing on his mind."

msgctxt "2152_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm sure he was more than happy to keep his head down and\r\n"
"let Kamurocho be Kamurocho."
msgstr "I'm sure he was more than happy to keep his head down and\r\n"
"let Kamurocho be Kamurocho."

msgctxt "2164_Akiyama"
msgid "For sure. That's why Arai-san and Kido-chan were so careful\r\n"
"not to make any waves."
msgstr "For sure. That's why Arai-san and Kido-chan were so careful\r\n"
"not to make any waves."

msgctxt "2176_Akiyama"
msgid "But yeah. Kido-chan's a monster."
msgstr "But yeah. Kido-chan's a monster."

msgctxt "2188_Date"
msgid "You think he let himself get kidnapped on purpose, then?"
msgstr "You think he let himself get kidnapped on purpose, then?"

msgctxt "2200_Akiyama"
msgid "You bet I do. By the time I got back to the office that day,\r\n"
"he was already gone."
msgstr "You bet I do. By the time I got back to the office that day,\r\n"
"he was already gone."

msgctxt "2212_Akiyama"
msgid "The place was more of a mess than usual thanks to the\r\n"
"\"struggle.\" It was convincing, honestly. But one thing stood out to me."
msgstr "The place was more of a mess than usual thanks to the\r\n"
"\"struggle.\" It was convincing, honestly. But one thing stood out to me."

msgctxt "2224_Tanimura"
msgid "Which was what?"
msgstr "Which was what?"

msgctxt "2236_Akiyama"
msgid "The order my books were in."
msgstr "The order my books were in."

msgctxt "2248_Tanimura"
msgid "Your... books?"
msgstr "Your... books?"

msgctxt "2260_Akiyama"
msgid "Yup. Kido-chan tossed a bunch of them around, probably to\r\n"
"make it look like a fight went down. Cover his tracks, you\r\n"
"know."
msgstr "Yup. Kido-chan tossed a bunch of them around, probably to\r\n"
"make it look like a fight went down. Cover his tracks, you\r\n"
"know."

msgctxt "2272_Akiyama"
msgid "But the ones that were still on the shelf weren't in the\r\n"
"right spots for some reason. That's how I knew something was up."
msgstr "But the ones that were still on the shelf weren't in the\r\n"
"right spots for some reason. That's how I knew something was up."

msgctxt "2284_Tanimura"
msgid "Hold on. Your office isn't exactly what I'd call organized.\r\n"
"Not by a long shot."
msgstr "Hold on. Your office isn't exactly what I'd call organized.\r\n"
"Not by a long shot."

msgctxt "2296_Tanimura"
msgid "Are you seriously telling me you know where every single\r\n"
"book is supposed to be on your shelf?"
msgstr "Are you seriously telling me you know where every single\r\n"
"book is supposed to be on your shelf?"

msgctxt "2308_Akiyama"
msgid "Every single one."
msgstr "Every single one."

msgctxt "2320_Tanimura"
msgid "Whoa..."
msgstr "Guau..."

msgctxt "2332_Akiyama"
msgid "Long story short, my old pal Kido-chan pulled a fast one on\r\n"
"me."
msgstr "Long story short, my old pal Kido-chan pulled a fast one on\r\n"
"me."

msgctxt "2344_Date"
msgid "What I really wanna know is, who keeps a hundred billion in\r\n"
"cash just lying around in this day and age?"
msgstr "What I really wanna know is, who keeps a hundred billion in\r\n"
"cash just lying around in this day and age?"

msgctxt "2356_Date"
msgid "Why not stash it in a bank?"
msgstr "Why not stash it in a bank?"

msgctxt "2368_Akiyama"
msgid "Don't trust 'em. Besides, it's not like any of them pay\r\n"
"decent interest anyway."
msgstr "Don't trust 'em. Besides, it's not like any of them pay\r\n"
"decent interest anyway."

msgctxt "2380_Kiryu"
msgid "That much physical money isn't exactly portable, though. How\r\n"
"did they get it all out?"
msgstr "That much physical money isn't exactly portable, though. How\r\n"
"did they get it all out?"

msgctxt "2392_Akiyama"
msgid "Ask the \"DA\" guys who raided my office yesterday. They're\r\n"
"the ones who did it."
msgstr "Ask the \"DA\" guys who raided my office yesterday. They're\r\n"
"the ones who did it."

msgctxt "2404_Tanimura"
msgid "You think they were impostors?"
msgstr "You think they were impostors?"

msgctxt "2416_Akiyama"
msgid "Big time. Katsuragi must've sent them over once Kido-chan\r\n"
"tipped him off."
msgstr "Big time. Katsuragi must've sent them over once Kido-chan\r\n"
"tipped him off."

msgctxt "2428_Kiryu"
msgid "That would explain it."
msgstr "That would explain it."

